{"tid":667770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★微軟傳以廉價 Surface 平板對撼 iPad","createTime":"2018-05-17T04:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T13:24:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"da266779a2dfb9d38ffcd3e16212105218deb4b4","tid":667770,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:33:27.000Z","msg":"較早前 Apple 推出針對教育市場的全新 9.7 吋 iPad，香港的售價只需 2,588 港元起，據說 Microsoft 亦準備推出全新的平價 Surface 平板迎戰。率先報導此消息的彭博表示，平價版 Surface 並非單純將現時的 Surface Pro 縮小和減價，而是一部全新設計的平板。<br />\n<br />\n最大改動相信是採用 10 吋屏幕，而非 Surface Pro 的 12 吋，機身不再採用現時的方正線條，而是改為類似 iPad 的圓角設計。平價 Surface 會以 USB-C 接口充電，而且售價為 400 美元（約 3,140 港元），貼近剛上市的 9.7 吋 iPad 的定價。彭博指評價 Surface 平板較現時 Surface Pro 輕約 20%，電池使用時間亦相對少 4 小時。<br />\n<br />\n報導指平價 Surface 平板會採用 Intel 處理器和圖像顯示，亦會使用完整版的 Windows 10 Pro 系統。Microsoft 打算跟 iPad 一樣提供兩個版本，分別為 Wi-Fi 版和 4G LTE 版本。雖然 Microsoft 沒有打算隨機附送鍵盤或手寫筆，但 Surface Pro 的機背支架設計將得以保留，而 Microsoft 亦會推出一批配合新機使用的鍵盤、手寫筆和滑鼠配件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/17/microsoft-consider-cheap-surface-to-compete-with-ipad/notebook/tablet-notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2Fmicrosoft-consider-cheap-surface-to-compete-with-ipad%2Fnotebook%2Ftablet-notebook%2F&d=28MNBqwg5GCie43WYRViMgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=71ff6494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/17/microsoft-consider-cheap-surface-to-compete-with-ipad/notebook/tablet-notebook/</a>"},{"pid":"7d2d2d0bc6450676e17da1b0182d91c5626efa80","tid":667770,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"apple die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125a40bf91fe3557a4b0ab875c755f3d3f7b93a8","tid":667770,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T04:35:14.